---
Title: This Union
By: 6e692c9a-52ef-49c0-a8c5-4ab5e733a7cd
Source:
  - Title: The Gift
    Page: 142
---
This
Union you want
With the earth and sky,
This union we all need with love,
A golden wing from God's heart just
Touched the ground,
Now
Step upon it
With your brave sun-vows
And help our eyes
To
Dance!
